name: Deep Agents
description: Deep Agents is a suite of AI-driven on-chain agents built on the Solana blockchain. The project focuses on processing blockchain and social data in real-time, providing traders and communities with actionable insights, automated strategies, and execution capabilities. Each agent is optimized for a critical task: from top-holder and whale behavior analysis to social sentiment monitoring, trading automation, and liquidity management. Deep Agents combines AI with Solana’s high-speed infrastructure to create an intelligence layer that simplifies decision-making and enhances transparency in token markets. The project’s mission is to make blockchain activity more understandable, reliable, and tradable through AI-powered agents.
